content: standujar: Focused on bug fixes and feature development, merging two PRs in elizaos/elizaos.github.io (#166, #165) that included a significant revert and subsequent fix for environment validation, while also opening two new feature PRs for JSON leaderboard API endpoints. Their work involved modifying 123 files with a primary focus on bugfix work (44%) and feature work (22%), touching code (53%), config (26%), and tests (15%).
